ta-tracking-container=3D"true"> <h3 class=3D"mntl-sc-block-universal-callou=
t__heading">Key Takeaways</h3>
<div class=3D"mntl-sc-block-universal-callout__body"><ul><li>Measuring ingr=
edients by weight (in grams) is often more accurate than using cups, especi=
ally for dry ingredients like flour.</li><li>Different ingredients have dif=
ferent conversion rates from grams to cups due to varying densities; for ex=
ample, 1 cup of flour is about 125 grams, while 1 cup of butter is 227 gram=
s.</li><li>Online conversion calculators and charts can be useful tools for=
 ensuring accurate baking measurements.<br></li></ul></div>
</div>
<p id=3D"mntl-sc-block_2-0" class=3D"comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-html"=
> Picture this: You are face-to-face with a recipe that lists ingredient am=
ounts in grams, but you have only ever measured in cups. Suddenly, you=E2=
=80=99re in unfamiliar territory. How are you supposed to know how many cup=
s are in 125 grams of flour? And how many cups of butter do you need for 20=
0 grams?&nbsp;
</p>
<div id=3D"mntl-sc-block_3-0" class=3D"comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-ads=
lot mntl-block"></div>
<p id=3D"mntl-sc-block_4-0" class=3D"comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-html"=
> Fortunately, there is a relatively easy way to make grams-to-cup conversi=
ons without messing up the cake,&nbsp;<a href=3D"https://www.southernliving=
.com/homemade-brownies-7253342" data-component=3D"link" data-source=3D"inli=
neLink" data-type=3D"internalLink" data-ordinal=3D"1">homemade brownies</a>=
, or&nbsp;<a href=3D"https://www.southernliving.com/food/bread/dough" data-=
component=3D"link" data-source=3D"inlineLink" data-type=3D"internalLink" da=
ta-ordinal=3D"2">loaf of bread</a>, and we are here to help demystify this =
process. After all, accurate ingredient measurement is crucial for producin=
g excellent baked goods, homemade pasta, and birthday cakes. We did the mat=
h for you. Here's how to handle baking conversions.
</p>
<div id=3D"mntl-sc-block_5-0" class=3D"comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-ads=
